{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"这妓院的生意似乎并不好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"只是今夜不好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"我要来这妓院搜查一事已传了开去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":320,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"这里的地方虽小，人可不少，嘴巴很多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"聪明人也很多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"昨夜出现的僵尸，是不是也是一个原因？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"我看就是了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"你的胆子并不大。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"本来就不大。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":10,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"你真的相信有僵尸这样的东西存在？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"我那个手下毫无疑问是给活生生吓死的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"并不一定僵尸才可吓死人。你那个手下，一个人私自转回，绝不会没有原因。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":348,"line_end":348},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"也许他有所发现。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"为什么你不说他看中了铁恨口中的辟毒珠？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"那样的一颗珠子，你可知什么价值？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":364,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"价值连城。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"是不是足以引人犯罪？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"我那个手下为人的确有些贪心。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"最低限度还有个人知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":398,"line_end":398},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"你是说王风？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":400,"line_end":400}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":500,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"他一定知道，问题只是他肯不肯说老实话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"在我的面前，没有人敢不说老实话。","tone":"严肃","chapter":10,"line_start":404,"line_end":404},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"他是不是还在鹦鹉楼？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"今早，我找他问话的时候还在。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"你就是血奴？","tone":"微笑","chapter":10,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"嗯。","tone":"微笑","chapter":10,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"听说你向来只穿一半衣服。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"这是事实。","tone":"微笑","chapter":10,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"现在你穿得很整齐。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"因为我怕着凉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"这几天都差不多，并不冷。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"你也怕僵尸？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我只是一个女孩子。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"那干嘛你不离开，还留在这里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":480,"line_end":480},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我没有地方好去。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":10,"line_start":482,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"李大娘哪里不好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"如果好我根本就不会来这里。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":10,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"王风不肯将这副棺材搬走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":500,"line_end":500}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":501,"line_end":600,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我没有问他，今天早上一时间又想不起。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"整整的一天，他去了什么地方？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":10,"line_start":504,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":506,"line_end":506},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"一句话也没有留下？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"他曾经说过去找他朋友的尸体。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":510,"line_end":510},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"铁恨的僵尸？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":512,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":518,"line_end":518},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"他是个巫师？也懂得降魔捉鬼？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":524,"line_end":524},{"speaker":"char_an_zi_hao","speaker_name":"安子豪","listener":null,"text":"在楼下，楼梯后面的小屋子里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"检验那棺材一个人已足够。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":560,"line_end":560}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_tang_lao_da","name":"唐老大","alias":[],"identity":"常笑手下官差","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":null,"rank":null,"one_line":"常笑手下的官差，擅长辨识毒药","personality":{"traits":["谨慎","干练","服从","细致","务实"],"speech_style":null,"temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_chang_xiao","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"服从"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[1