{"segment":8,"line_start":701,"line_end":800,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你什么时候变做僵尸的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":712,"line_end":712},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你都看到了？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":10,"line_start":718,"line_end":718},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_xue_nu","text":"那时候我还没有睡着。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":720,"line_end":720},{"speaker":"char_xue_nu","speaker_name":"血奴","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"打死你，打死你——","tone":"激动","chapter":10,"line_start":730,"line_end":730},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":null,"text":"住手！","tone":"厉声","chapter":10,"line_start":742,"line_end":742},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"十年前我就已做官。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":10,"line_start":756,"line_end":756},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"怪不得你的嗓门这么大。","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":758,"line_end":758},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你不怕官？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":760,"line_end":760},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我又没有犯法，为什么要怕官。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":10,"line_start":762,"line_end":762},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你躲在棺材里干什么？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":764,"line_end":764},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"睡觉。","tone":"平静","chapter":10,"line_start":766,"line_end":766},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"这里有三丈宽的大床。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":768,"line_end":768},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我就算不睡在床上，只睡在棺材里，也好像不犯法。","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":770,"line_end":770},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"吓人就犯法了。","tone":"严肃","chapter":10,"line_start":772,"line_end":772},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我没有吓人，只不过从睡觉的地方跳出来。你属下的胆子，似乎并不大。","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":774,"line_end":776},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你的胆子却不小。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":10,"line_start":778,"line_end":778},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"本来就不小。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":10,"line_start":780,"line_end":780},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"怪不得敢胆在棺材里面睡觉。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":782,"line_end":782},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"不敢也要敢。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":784,"line_end":784},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你知不知道棺材是用来放死人的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":786,"line_end":786},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"知道。","tone":"平静","chapter":10,"line_start":788,"line_end":788},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你知不知道这棺材已睡过死人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":790,"line_end":790},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"知道。","tone":"平静","chapter":10,"line_start":792,"line_end":792},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"什么都知道，你这是喜欢棺材的了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":794,"line_end":794},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"不喜欢。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":796,"line_end":796},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"不喜欢为什么要睡进去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":798,"line_end":798},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我没有地方好睡。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":800,"line_end":800}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_wang_feng","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":702,"line_end":800,"text":"王风躲在棺材中假扮僵尸"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":9,"line_start":801,"line_end":904,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"这张床也不好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":802,"line_end":802},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"对别人很好，但对我却不好。今天早上我实在太疲倦，除非不睡，一睡势必就像死人一样。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":804,"line_end":804},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"所以你索性就睡进棺材？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":808,"line_end":808},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"这并不是真正的原因。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":810,"line_end":810},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"真正的原因是什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":812,"line_end":812},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我不想这么快就真的变成死人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":814,"line_end":814},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"有人要杀你？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":10,"line_start":816,"line_end":816},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"有，昨天就已有四个，真正要杀我的却不是他们。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":818,"line_end":818},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"他们只是四个刽子手？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":820,"line_end":820},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我看就是了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":822,"line_end":822},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你到底开罪了什么人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":824,"line_end":824},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"什么人我也没有开罪，他们要杀我也许就因为我留在这里，因为我是一个聪明人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":826,"line_end":828},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"据我所知聪明人的确都不怎样长命。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":830,"line_end":830},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"有时是的。","tone":"平静","chapter":10,"line_start":832,"line_end":832},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"有时是指什么时候？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":834,"line_end":834},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"当他让别人都觉得他有点危险的时候。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":836,"line_end":836},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"一个人使人有危险感觉，一定不会受欢迎。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":840,"line_end":840},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"那种方法的确好，我也时常用。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":846,"line_end":846},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"好办法未必就一定有效。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":848,"line_end":848},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"如果他们发觉你死人一样睡着，那就会有效的了。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":850,"line_end":850},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"所以我只有睡进棺材。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":852,"line_end":852},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"好在那副棺材曾经走出过一具僵尸。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":858,"line_end":858},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"可惜就连这种地方我也只能睡一次。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":866,"line_end":866},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"你怕死？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":872,"line_end":872},{"speaker":"char_chang_xiao","speaker_name":"常笑","listener":"char_wang_feng","text":"我看你简直就怕得很。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":10,"line_start":876,"line_end":876},{"speaker":"char_wang_feng","speaker_name":"王风","listener":"char_chang_xiao","text":"我只是不想死得不明不白。死有什么可怕？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":10,"line_start":878,"line_end":878}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
